   17: -module(app_SUITE).
   18: 
   19: -compile([export_all]).
   20: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   21: 
   22: suite() ->
   23:     [{ct_hooks, [ts_install_cth]}].
   24: 
   25: all() ->
   26:     [app, appup].
   27: 
   28: groups() ->
   29:     [].
   30: 
   31: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   32:     Config.
   33: 
   34: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   35:      ok.
   36: 
   37: init_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   38:     Config.
   39: 
   40: end_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   41:     Config.
   42: 
   43: app() ->
   44:     [{doc, "Test that the parsetools app file is ok"}].
   45: app(Config) when is_list(Config) ->
   46:     ok = test_server:app_test(parsetools).
   47: 
   48: appup() ->
   49:     [{doc, "Test that the parsetools appup file is ok"}].
   50: appup(Config) when is_list(Config) ->
   51:     ok = test_server:appup_test(parsetools).
